    <title>Water contributor: Cindy Wallis-Lage</title>
    <description>Cindy Wallis-Lage is president of Black &amp;amp; Veatch’s Water Business, leading the company’s efforts to address billions of dollars in water infrastructure needs around the world. Wallis-Lage joined the company in 1987 and has provided technical and management leadership expertise to more than 100 projects worldwide. Wallis-Lage joined the Black &amp;amp; Veatch Board of Directors in 2012 and is currently on the Board of Directors for the US Water Alliance.
</description>
